result.name: McDonald's

reviews.text: Place not clean as lack of man power. Fast on puchasing

Horrible!

Being a vegetarian I thankfully avoid McDonald’s. But, on this winter afternoon, I had a craving for French Fries so I went into McDonald’s with my wife. 

We were served COLD, white and limp looking French Fries...My wife asked them for a hot replacement and they brought it fresh out of fryer and served us. IT WAS STILL NOT WARM, FORGET HOT. 

I wonder how McDonald’s can get away with selling rubbish, food not worth eating. I would not consider those cold limp French Fries as food. 

It’s not the first time I had a bad experience with McDonald’s on food temperature! It appears to be their policy for years to cook food at lower temperature so that more customers can be fed rubbish and more dollars can come into McDonald’s fast!
Staffs are rude, serving is very slow, especially after they implemented the order-calling system, the execution is simply disaster. Probably the worst McDonald’s in Hong Kong.
Disappointed by not proper warming burger, cockroaches found in consuming area,poor hygiene
stupid waitress force.people to buy

reviews.text: 出餐極慢，員工態度差，食物質素以其他麥當勞分店來說是最差，我找不到一間可以比這一間更差；而這裡Mac Cafe就相當好，員工及食物水準都可以保持良好質素。每一次堂食及外賣的體驗相當差，外賣熱香餅常欠牛油糖膠，冰檸茶得大半杯，問員工有無野可以篤檸檬，佢就掉支木棒，態度如常地差。
任何時間都咁多人。 特別係細路
點餐機前手機信號較弱

職員好煩, 令到用餐感覺差。
多做事少說話比較好。
港式奶菜完全吾得！
